                        <h1>October 28, 2009</h1>                                  
                        New technologies emerge at the speed of light, but are they all buzzworthy? Market-makers? Consumer must-haves? Or are they soon to be yesterday's news? Learn where you can unearth the answers to these questions in this edition of CES Up to the Minute. And if you haven't registered for the 2010 CES, January 7-10 in Las Vegas, Nevada, <A href="/register">do it now to save $100 from the on-site registration fee</A>. Because when your boss is happy, everyone's happy. 

