<a name="3472"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Build Your Event Plan and Get Organized for CES </div>
<br />
<IMG hspace=5 align=left src="/print/images/content/MyCES_172.gif" width=172 height=67>Whether you're searching for exhibitors, products or sessions that interest you or meet your business needs, the MyCES Personal Planner organizes your search results when you add them to your Event Plan. It's the best way to get organized as you plan the four most important days of your business year. Just think: You'll know what you're doing and where you're going each day so you won't waste time trying to figure it out once you arrive at the show. It's like having your personalized Outlook calendar at your fingertips.&nbsp; <BR><BR><A href="/print/myCES.asp">Learn about MyCES.<BR></A><BR><A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/account/login.aspx">Create your 2010 MyCES account today!</A> <BR><BR>Already have a MyCES account? <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/account/login.aspx">Login now.</A> <BR>

